    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>in 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> and set aside to infuse – this is your <strong>creamy paprika stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
